@startuml API请求处理时序图

' 考点：UML 时序图 (Sequence Diagram)
' 描述：用户调用工具 API 的完整请求处理流程
' 作者：architect-exam-lab

title 在线工具聚合平台 - API 请求处理时序图\n（用户调用工具 API 完整流程）

skinparam sequenceMessageAlignment center
skinparam sequence {
  ArrowColor DarkBlue
  ActorBorderColor DarkBlue
  LifeLineBorderColor DarkBlue
  ParticipantBackgroundColor LightYellow
  ParticipantBorderColor DarkOrange
}

actor "用户\n(Client)" as Client
participant "API Gateway\n:3000" as Gateway
participant "认证中间件\n(Auth MW)" as AuthMW
participant "限流中间件\n(Rate Limiter)" as RateLimiter
participant "熔断器\n(Circuit Breaker)" as CB
participant "Auth Service\n:3001" as AuthSvc
participant "Tool Registry\n:3002" as Registry
participant "Redis\n(Cache)" as Redis
database "PostgreSQL\n(DB)" as DB

== 第一阶段：用户登录，获取 Token ==

Client -> Gateway: POST /auth/login\n{email, password}
activate Gateway

Gateway -> AuthMW: 检查是否需要认证
note right of AuthMW: /auth/login 路径\n无需 Token 认证

Gateway -> AuthSvc: POST /login\n{email, password}
activate AuthSvc

AuthSvc -> DB: findUserByEmail(email)
activate DB
DB --> AuthSvc: User 记录
deactivate DB

AuthSvc -> AuthSvc: bcrypt.compare(password, hash)
note right of AuthSvc: 验证密码\n约 100ms（bcrypt cost=12）

AuthSvc -> AuthSvc: jwt.sign({userId, role}, secret, {expiresIn: '15m'})
note right of AuthSvc: 生成 Access Token（15分钟有效期）\n生成 Refresh Token（7天有效期）

AuthSvc -> DB: saveRefreshToken(userId, refreshToken)
activate DB
DB --> AuthSvc: 保存成功
deactivate DB

AuthSvc --> Gateway: {accessToken, refreshToken}
deactivate AuthSvc

Gateway --> Client: 200 OK\n{accessToken, refreshToken}
deactivate Gateway

== 第二阶段：携带 Token 调用工具 API ==

Client -> Gateway: GET /tools/text-converter/execute\nAuthorization: Bearer <accessToken>\n{text: "Hello World"}
activate Gateway

' 中间件 1：认证验证
Gateway -> AuthMW: 验证 JWT Token
activate AuthMW
AuthMW -> AuthMW: jwt.verify(token, secret)
note right of AuthMW: 只验证签名和过期时间\n不查询数据库（无状态）

alt Token 无效或已过期
  AuthMW --> Gateway: 401 Unauthorized
  Gateway --> Client: 401 Unauthorized\n{error: "Token 无效"}
end

AuthMW --> Gateway: {userId, role} 用户信息注入 request
deactivate AuthMW

' 中间件 2：限流检查
Gateway -> RateLimiter: 检查令牌桶\nkey: ip:192.168.1.1
activate RateLimiter
RateLimiter -> Redis: GET rate-limit:ip:192.168.1.1
activate Redis
Redis --> RateLimiter: 令牌数 = 85（< 100，未超限）
deactivate Redis

RateLimiter -> Redis: DECR rate-limit:ip:192.168.1.1
activate Redis
Redis --> RateLimiter: 84
deactivate Redis

RateLimiter --> Gateway: 通过（剩余 84 次）
deactivate RateLimiter

' 中间件 3：熔断器检查
Gateway -> CB: 检查 tool-registry 熔断状态
activate CB
CB -> CB: circuitBreaker.state == CLOSED（正常）
CB --> Gateway: 允许通过
deactivate CB

' 路由：查询工具注册信息
Gateway -> Redis: GET toollab:tool:text-converter
activate Redis

alt 缓存命中
  Redis --> Gateway: Tool 元数据（JSON）
  note right of Redis: 缓存命中！\n直接返回，无需查询 Registry
else 缓存未命中
  Redis --> Gateway: null
  deactivate Redis

  Gateway -> Registry: GET /tools/text-converter
  activate Registry

  Registry -> DB: findToolByName('text-converter')
  activate DB
  DB --> Registry: Tool 记录
  deactivate DB

  Registry --> Gateway: Tool 元数据\n{endpoint: "http://tool-service:3010", ...}
  deactivate Registry

  Gateway -> Redis: SETEX toollab:tool:text-converter 300 <json>
  activate Redis
  note right of Redis: 缓存 5 分钟（TTL=300s）
  Redis --> Gateway: OK
  deactivate Redis
end

' 代理请求到工具服务
Gateway -> Gateway: http-proxy → tool-service:3010
note right of Gateway: 反向代理请求\n携带用户信息头部：\nX-User-Id: user123\nX-User-Role: USER

Gateway --> Client: 200 OK\n{success: true, data: {result: "HELLO WORLD"}}
deactivate Gateway

== 第三阶段：Token 过期，刷新 Token ==

Client -> Gateway: POST /auth/refresh\nCookie: refreshToken=<token>
activate Gateway
Gateway -> AuthSvc: POST /refresh\n{refreshToken}
activate AuthSvc
AuthSvc -> DB: findRefreshToken(token)
activate DB
DB --> AuthSvc: 有效
deactivate DB
AuthSvc -> AuthSvc: 生成新的 Access Token
AuthSvc --> Gateway: {accessToken: <new-token>}
deactivate AuthSvc
Gateway --> Client: 200 OK\n{accessToken: <new-token>}
deactivate Gateway

@enduml
